        <p>After two succesfull editions in 2024 and 2025, the industry track is here to stay! The only difference in 2026? The track will be <b>even bigger and better!</b> </p>
        <p>
            Its still the <b>must-attend track for decision makers</b> exploring the adoption of Rust in their
            organisation, but in 2026 the <b>track's talks will be open to all vistors of RustWeek</b> to attend. 
        </p>
        <p>
            Date & time: <strong>Tuesday 19 May, 9:30 - 16:30 CET</strong>.<br>
            (Exact duration to be communicated)
        </p>
        <h3>City & venue</h3>
        <p>
            Kinepolis Jaarbeurs Utrecht, <br /> Jaarbeursboulevard 300, <br /> 3521
